{"tid":290661,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"琴晚甜品 試整飲食台大熱檸檬撻","createTime":"2017-06-20T02:45:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T03:57:39.000Z","uid":18117,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a5cbc669453a8d8abd022c9623c79d8de46c05d3","tid":290661,"uid":18117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:45:45.000Z","msg":"見依排檸檬撻係連登咁hit我都跟住做<br />\n第一次整撻類既野 個皮做得唔夠鬆同厚左少少<br />\n其次係個餡 整果陣覺得太稀驚會唔凝固 <br />\n跟住落左啲魚膠粉點知又重手左少少<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/095137_f013dcd04e3188a9dbc3111f98172260.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F095137_f013dcd04e3188a9dbc3111f98172260.jpg&h=712d40d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n總括黎講都幾易整 <br />\n下次自己再調整下份量就完美<br />\n屋企人都意外地好中意食<br />\n因為酸酸甜甜好撚開胃 <br />\n老豆好少食甜品都一口氣啪左兩件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://icook.tw/recipes/205237\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ficook.tw%2Frecipes%2F205237&d=YgJuT%2F1eacVT0fIfCeo4ob%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=0bc742b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://icook.tw/recipes/205237</a><br />\n食譜我跟依個 做左double份量 <br />\n最後做左12隻細撻加1隻大撻<br />\n<br />\n成本<br />\n牛油$25<br />\n檸檬4隻$12<br />\n雞蛋4隻$10<br />\n糖, 麵粉, 杏仁粉, 奶 份量少好難計 加埋當$20<br />\n人工$50/h 前後大概用左3個鐘=$150<br />\ntotal=$217"},{"pid":"baad9faef48fdc298d99040ba5c95e9d780a2c2a","tid":290661,"uid":43285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T02:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有雪櫃錢呢? 地價補左未?"},{"pid":"906c7873c5f44ea97e62f591e3c52236c726681b","tid":290661,"uid":25899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit